WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.533 --> 00:00:08.366
The thief's mission to the county seat is done

2
00:00:08.366 --> 00:00:09.400
So happy

3
00:00:12.466 --> 00:00:13.566
What about people?

4
00:00:14.166 --> 00:00:14.966
Come to me

5
00:00:15.466 --> 00:00:17.700
What the hell are you doing up there?

6
00:00:17.700 --> 00:00:18.866
Scared to death

7
00:00:18.933 --> 00:00:20.400
Didn't you ask me to fix the roof?

8
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:21.766
You fix the roof?

9
00:00:22.100 --> 00:00:23.566
Then why didn't you fix it before?

10
00:00:23.566 --> 00:00:24.633
I'm lazy

11
00:00:24.666 --> 00:00:26.566
Then why did I ask you to fix it and you fixed it?

12
00:00:26.566 --> 00:00:28.200
If you ask me to fix it or not

13
00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:29.866
You'll have to come up and fix the roof yourself

14
00:00:29.866 --> 00:00:31.200
You are so skinny

15
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:32.366
Underdeveloped limbs

16
00:00:32.533 --> 00:00:33.466
At that time

17
00:00:33.700 --> 00:00:36.133
It must have fallen from the beam.

18
00:00:36.133 --> 00:00:37.300
I have to take care of you

19
00:00:37.300 --> 00:00:39.600
I don't want to trouble myself.

20
00:00:39.733 --> 00:00:42.333
I knew you weren't so kind

21
00:00:42.333 --> 00:00:43.300
Get down here!

22
00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:46.200
I bought you something nice. Why?

23
00:00:47.700 --> 00:00:49.233
For me, yeah?

24
00:00:49.366 --> 00:00:50.900
Didn't you fix the roof?

25
00:00:50.900 --> 00:00:51.900
Earn your wages

26
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.200
Two bucks a pair.

27
00:00:53.200 --> 00:00:55.600
So you went to the county seat and bought me a pair of shoes on purpose

28
00:00:55.666 --> 00:00:57.966
I also bought a wedding wine for Lao Zhishu and Brother Hua Zi

29
00:00:57.966 --> 00:00:58.566
Happy Candy

30
00:00:58.566 --> 00:01:01.100
After all, they have helped us so much

31
00:01:01.133 --> 00:01:03.300
Come down and see if it fits

32
00:01:04.900 --> 00:01:07.300
Tonight we have eel porridge

33
00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:11.300
This little spy actually found my shoes

34
00:01:11.300 --> 00:01:13.000
I can't wear it anymore

35
00:01:13.166 --> 00:01:15.666
That was pretty careful work.

